</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>offset</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Starting bit position to test and set </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>to_set</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>if true the region will be set if all bits are cleared if false the region will be cleard if all bits are set</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<parameterlist kind="retval"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>0</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Operation successful </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>-EINVAL</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Invalid argument (e.g. bit to set exceeds the number of bits in bit array, etc.) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>-EEXIST</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>at least one bit in the region is set/cleared, operation cancelled </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
